73
00:06:45,879 --> 00:06:47,800
And I've already missed her.

74
00:06:49,879 --> 00:06:52,240
I think I heard you say

75
00:06:53,839 --> 00:06:55,199
that you can never see

76
00:06:55,319 --> 00:06:56,360
