and that of Crimson Clan.

111
00:10:32,639 --> 00:10:34,320
There's no such thing as a coincidence.

112
00:10:34,720 --> 00:10:35,879
If you can't do it,

113
00:10:36,360 --> 00:10:37,320
I'll do it for you.

114
00:10:52,639 --> 00:10:53,600
What's wrong with you?

115
